    {
      "chinese": "在Sinabal那個地方，有通道可以進到長尾人那邊拜訪，人們已經三次到那邊拜訪。長尾人的住處很遠，要背一簍筐的松樹材，點燃以照明晚間要走的路。",
      "ab": "Ihan “Sinabal” ta heza laqaiban maqtu mungkumbu’ han doqpus visvis ta tantungu, muti’unin nat bunun se’ita tantungu. Daqvisan cia doqpus visvis sat dangi’an, asa tu mama’ ’i taspalangan tu cang ispalcioq maca maqmut mudadan.",
      "order": "2",
      "sound": "https://dzywvpqnys6mw.cloudfront.net/files/2023/01/02/ad8a6b3a8e70a24466d8d5bcd06c3a56.wav",
